t-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-3-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-3-150x100.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-3.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis is an easy, classic risotto with lots of parmesan and super creamy mascarpone cheese. It might just be my favorite one yet because it is soooo ridiculously creamy. Melty, creamy and a great neutral dish to pair with some many things. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"mascarpone risotto with seared filet mignon\" width=\"1663\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Mascarpone Risotto with Seared Filet Mignon.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-scaled.jpg 1663w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-728x963.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-768x1016.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-1161x1536.jpg 1161w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-1548x2048.jpg 1548w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-150x198.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1663px) 100vw, 1663px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201663%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-scaled.jpg 1663w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-728x963.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-768x1016.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-1161x1536.jpg 1161w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-1548x2048.jpg 1548w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-150x198.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-12-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUp first: our favorite seared filet. This is Max’s favorite meal right now. Eddie loves filet, but we don’t have it very often. So serving it alongside this creamy rice makes for an amazing meal. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMy keys to making a perfect filet: a cast iron skillet, lots of kosher salt and pepper and a little bit of butter. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThat is all you need! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"mascarpone risotto with seared filet mignon\" width=\"1585\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Mascarpone Risotto with Seared Filet Mignon.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-scaled.jpg 1585w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-728x1011.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-768x1066.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-1106x1536.jpg 1106w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-1475x2048.jpg 1475w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-150x208.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1585px) 100vw, 1585px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201585%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-scaled.jpg 1585w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-728x1011.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-768x1066.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-1106x1536.jpg 1106w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-1475x2048.jpg 1475w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-150x208.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI usually also include some sort of roasted veggie with this. Like \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2019/01/parmesan-roasted-broccoli/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emy favorite roasted broccoli\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e or asparagus or green beans. Or even \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2016/01/howsweeteats-house-salad/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ea house salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e before. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"mascarpone risotto with seared filet mignon\" width=\"1698\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Mascarpone Risotto with Seared Filet Mignon.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-scaled.jpg 1698w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-728x943.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-768x995.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-1185x1536.jpg 1185w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-1580x2048.jpg 1580w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1698px) 100vw, 1698px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201698%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-scaled.jpg 1698w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-728x943.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-768x995.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-1185x1536.jpg 1185w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-1580x2048.jpg 1580w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-10-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe love meals like this at home because they are unexpected and make a regular ordinary day dinner feel fabulous. A great one to make to feel loved, even by yourself! \u003cspan id=\"more-97834\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"mascarpone risotto with seared filet mignon\" width=\"1663\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Mascarpone Risotto with Seared Filet Mignon.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-scaled.jpg 1663w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-728x963.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-768x1016.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-1161x1536.jpg 1161w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-1548x2048.jpg 1548w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-150x198.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1663px) 100vw, 1663px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201663%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-scaled.jpg 1663w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-728x963.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-768x1016.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-1161x1536.jpg 1161w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-1548x2048.jpg 1548w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-150x198.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eMascarpone Risotto with Seared Filet Mignon\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-97848\" data-recipe-id=\"97848\" data-servings=\"0\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-11-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eMascarpone Risotto with Seared Filet\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e45\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis mascarpone risotto is a fancy and fun meal to make at home. The ingredients and flavors are simple yet decadent, pleasing to everyone. This is a classic comfort food dish, but one that can really elevate a meal at home too!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97848\" data-servings=\"0\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003erisotto\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echicken or vegetable stock\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 ½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003earborio rice\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic cloves,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eminced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¾\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/prophecy-pinot-grigio-white-wine-750ml-bottle/-/A-51494687?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edry white wine,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003elike sauvignon blanc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/kraft-100-grated-parmesan-cheese-8oz/-/A-12958582?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efinely grated parmesan cheese\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003emascarpone cheese\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003efresh chives,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003esteaks\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"11\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efilet mignon steaks,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eabout 2 inches thick\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"12\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and fresh ground pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"13\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2 to 3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/land-o-lakes-unsalted-butter-1lb/-/A-13227053?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eunsalted butter\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97848\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003erisotto\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn a large saucepan, heat the stock on low until it’s warm.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn another saucepan or stock pot, heat the remaining tablespoon of olive oil on medium-low heat. Stir in the garlic and rice with a big pinch of salt and pepper. Cook, stirring often, to toast the rice for 3 to 5 minutes. The rice should be translucent.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eOnce the rice is translucent, stir in the white wine (or you can just use extra stock). Cook until the wine has been absorbed. Add 1 cup of the warm stock, stirring continuously, until the stock is absorbed. Repeat again with 1 cup of stock, stirring until absorbed. Repeat this process with another 2 to 3 cups of the stock, until the rice is creamy and al dente. You want it to appear “hydrated” – and want there to be some liquid left when serving. This process should take about 15 to 20 minutes or even a few minutes longer.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile I’m stirring, I make the steaks! I have them out beforehand, and sear them on the burner next to the risotto.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen the risotto is plump and ready, stir in the parmesan and the mascarpone. Stir continuously until both melt.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen ready to serve, top with the fresh herbs, a little fresh parmesan and fresh cracked black pepper. Serve with the filet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003esteaks\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreheat the oven to 450 degrees F. I highly highly suggest using a cast iron skillet for this - it will get a little smoky, so be sure to use your oven vent or turn on a fan, etc!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-1-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat a cast iron skillet over medium-high heat. Season the steaks all over with salt and fresh ground pepper. Add the 2 tablespoons of butter to the skillet - it will begin to brown and smoke. That’s okay!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-1-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlace the steak in the skillet right away. Sear on each side, about 2 minutes per side, until deeply golden brown. Add the remaining tablespoon of butter if needed. Once you’ve done both sides, turn off the heat.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-1-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlace the skillet in the oven and cook for about 3 to 5 minutes, for medium doneness. This will depend on the thickness of your steak, but I suggest taking the internal temperature as this will help so much! For rare, you want 120 degrees F. For medium rare, 125 to 130 degrees F. For medium, 135 to 140 degrees F and medium-well, 145 to 150 degrees F.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97848-step-1-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eLet the steak rest for 5 to 10 minutes before slicing and serving with the risotto.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-13-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"mascarpone risotto with seared filet mignon\" width=\"1746\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Mascarpone Risotto with Seared Filet Mignon.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-13-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-13-scaled.jpg 1746w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-13-728x917.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-13-768x968.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-13-1219x1536.jpg 1219w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-13-1625x2048.jpg 1625w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mascarpone-risotto-and-filet-13-150x189.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1746px) 100vw, 1746px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\